The '''Feminist Peace Network''' (FPN) advocates for the human rights of women and raises awareness about [[misogyny]]  and the global pandemic of [[violence against women]] violence against women. In addition, FPN advocates and supports the active participation of women and the full reflection of women’s needs in the process of conflict resolution and the creation of sustainable peace  and examines many issues including education, health, economics, the environment and media from a gendered lens.

