'''Frank-Jürgen Richter''' (born 1967) is a German entrepreneur and chair of [[Horasis]]. He has served in that role since he founded the organization.

==Education and professional life==
After graduating with a degree in [[industrial engineering]] from the [[Karlsruhe Institute of Technology|University of Karlsruhe]] (now part of the Karlsruhe Institute of Technology) and academic stays in France and Mexico, Richter pursued his PhD-studies at the [[University of Tsukuba]] and obtained his doctoral degree from the [[University of Stuttgart]].

From 1996 until 2000, he lived and worked in Asia where he developed and managed a European Multinationals' Asian operations, and then became a Director of the [[World Economic Forum]] from 2001 to 2004.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldtradereview.com/news.asp?pType=N&iType=A&iID=70&siD=11&nID=11832 |title=The World Trade Review |publisher=The World Trade Review |date=15 November 2003 |accessdate=2014-08-14}}</ref> Following the incorporation of Horasis in 2005 he has been a frequent international traveler, researcher and commentator as well as leading the annual Business Meetings.

==Business meetings==
In 2005, Richter founded [[Horasis]], an independent think tank for global business topics.<ref>{{cite web|author=Horasis.org |url=http://www.horasis.org/newsweek%20_1.php |title=News :: The Continued Rise of the Rest |publisher=Horasis.org |date=18 November 2009 |accessdate=2014-08-14}}</ref> Richter works with businesspeople, politicians and intellectuals.<ref>{{cite web|author=17. November 2009 |url=http://www.wiwo.de/politik-weltwirtschaft/platzt-in-china-die-naechste-blase-413871/ |title=Konjunktur: Platzt in China die nächsteBlase? – Ausland – Politik – Wirtschaftswoche |language=de |publisher=Wiwo.de |date= |accessdate=2014-08-14}}</ref><ref name="youtube1">{{cite web|author=Global Asia TV |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W0YGLwkWYlI |title=ArkadyDvorkovich with Frank-Jurgen Richter, Chairman, Horasis |publisher=YouTube |date= |accessdate=2014-08-14}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.keminet.net/~minfagov/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=7480:ministri-i-puneve-te-jashtme-z-edmond-haxhinasto-priti-ne-takim-presidentin-e-horasis-&catid=112:lajme&Itemid=88&lang=en |title=The Minister of Foreign Affairs, Mr. Edmond Haxhinasto Received the President of " Horasis" |publisher=Keminet.net |date= |accessdate=2014-08-14}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.khaleejtimes.com/DisplayArticle08.asp?xfile=data/opinion/2011/October/opinion_October142.xml&section=opinion |title=Small is also beautiful |publisher=Khaleejtimes.com |date=29 October 2011 |accessdate=2014-08-14}}</ref> He advises governments and private sector organizations on issues such as globalization, trade, and sustainable development.<ref name="youtube1"/><ref>{{cite web|author=Horasis.org |url=http://www.horasis.org/press_releases_all_21.php |title=News :: China-Europe Connector |publisher=Horasis.org |date=22 September 2007 |accessdate=2014-08-14}}</ref>

==Commentary and publications==
Richter is a frequent public speaker.<ref>{{cite web|author=Horasis.org |url=http://www.horasis.org/press_releases_all_44.php |title=News :: Trade Protectionism |publisher=Horasis.org |date=23 November 2009 |accessdate=2014-08-14}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indiainfoline.com/Markets/News/Interview-with-Dr.-Frank-J%C3%BCrgen-Richter-Chairman-Horasis/5185843586 |title=Mutual funds step up selling |publisher=Indiainfoline.com |date= |accessdate=2014-08-14}}</ref> He has authored and edited 37 books and numerous articles on global strategy and Asian business,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/1596224274 |title=Six Billion Minds: Managing Outsourcing in the Global Knowledge Economy: Mark Minevich, Dr. Frank-Jürgen Richter, Faisal Hoque: 9781596224278: Amazon.com: Books |publisher=Amazon.com |date=30 April 2006 |accessdate=2014-08-14}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/0470821302 |title=Global Future: The Next Challenge for Asian Business: ArnoudDeMeyer, Peter Williamson, Frank-Jürgen Richter, Pamela C. M. Mar: 9780470821305: Amazon.com: Books |publisher=Amazon.com |date= |accessdate=2014-08-14}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/9812611967 |title=India Rising: Emergence of a New World Power: Colette Mathur, Frank-Jürgen Richter, Tarun Das: 9789812611963: Amazon.com: Books |publisher=Amazon.com |date=30 November 2005 |accessdate=2014-08-14}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/0470820861 |title=China: Enabling a New Era of Changes: Pamela C. M. Mar, Frank-Jürgen Richter: 9780470820865: Amazon.com: Books |publisher=Amazon.com |date=15 April 2003 |accessdate=2014-08-14}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Frank Richter (Author) |url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/1567203779 |title=The Asian Economic Catharsis: How Asian Firms Bounce Back from Crisis: Frank Richter: 9781567203776: Amazon.com: Books |publisher=Amazon.com |date=30 September 2000 |accessdate=2014-08-14}}</ref> covering topics such as the Asian business environment and how Asian firms bounced back from the 1998 Asian crisis. His writings have appeared in the financial and regional press such as [[The New York Times]].

He has addressed audiences at the [[Brookings Institution]], [[Harvard University]], [[Beijing University]], [[National Research University Higher School of Economics]], Moscow, [[Royal Institute of International Affairs]], and at several corporate events.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.urban-forum.com/frank_jurgen_richter.html |title=Frank-Jürgen Richter |publisher=Urban Forum |date=29 October 2011 |accessdate=2014-08-14}}</ref> He has been interviewed by several publications, and appeared on [[CNN]], [[BBC]], [[CNBC]], CCTV ([[China Central Television]]) as well as The Voice of America ([[VOA]]).<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.moneycontrol.com/news/fiiview/indiancompaniestobenefitfromeucrisisexpert_566547.html |title=Indian companies to benefit from EU crisis: Expert |publisher=Moneycontrol.com |date= |accessdate=2014-08-14}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Global Asia TV |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q_rLBs41B4w&feature=player_embedded#at=41 |title=Frank-Jürgen Richter, presidente de Horasis |publisher=YouTube |date= |accessdate=2014-08-14}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.cri.cn/4026/2008/10/28/1721s418754.htm |title=Interview with Dr. Frank Jurgen Richter, President of Horasis |publisher=English.cri.cn |date= |accessdate=2014-08-14}}</ref>

